1. *Mesecu* je potrebna svetlost da bi se osvetlio put. (The moon needs light to illuminate the path.)
2. U *mesecu* januaru, obično pada sneg. (In the month of January, it usually snows.)
3. Prošle godine sam otišao na more u *mesecu* avgustu. (Last year I went to the sea in the month of August.)
4. Zvezde na nebu sjaje svetlije kad nema *meseca*. (The stars in the sky shine brighter when there is no moon.)
5. U *mesecu* maju obično slavimo Dan majki. (In the month of May, we usually celebrate Mother's Day.)
6. *Mesecu* se često pripisuju mistična značenja u mnogim kulturama. (The moon is often attributed mystical meanings in many cultures.)
7. Prošlog *meseca* smo bili u poseti svojim rođacima u Beogradu. (Last month we visited our relatives in Belgrade.)
8. Uveče, *mesec* sija na nebu i pruža predivan prizor. (In the evening, the moon shines in the sky and provides a beautiful sight.)
9. *Mesec* je veoma važan za neke narode koji ga smatraju svetim. (The moon is very important for some people who consider it sacred.)
10. Želim da putujem po svetu i vidim *mesec* na različitim mestima. (I want to travel the world and see the moon in different places.)